description.value: While humans are social creatures, many humans need little more than a village of people to fill that need. Country humans were born into a lifestyle that felt no need for city luxuries or a fast-paced lifestyle. Raised instead to focus on family, friends, and hard work, country humans have a different view on life.

system.classDetails:
Country Human Traits

  • Compatibility: Hominoid
  • Skill Proficiency: You have proficiency in one skill from the following list: Athletics, Craft, Nature, Instinct.
  • Weapon Proficiency: You have proficiency in sickles, scythes, tridents, and whips.
